{"tid":2169330,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男友去外國讀master 好驚會同第個一齊","createTime":"2020-08-22T11:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T21:31:50.000Z","uid":100155,"like":4,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"3587647acbec889db28f13f14ab13b84a7d496c7","tid":2169330,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"本身都感情穩定 拍左年半<br />\n男友plan左去澳洲讀master<br />\n我因為想照顧屋企人唔打算跟佢過去 （可能會每兩三個星期飛過去/佢飛過黎見面）<br />\n<br />\n好驚佢識第個<br />\n人在外地會唔會好易同其他女仔一齊？<br />\n（喺香港已經成日有女仔dm佢 係覆完story會再開話題傾落去咁<br />\n佢話係大學同學 不過d對話好似都hea）<br />\n<br />\n其實我未去過澳洲 嗰度啲大學多唔多香港/亞洲女仔？（佢間u都係喺啲大城市）<br />\n<br />\n同埋不論男女 人在外國會唔會open啲？<br />\n佢本身唔係特別外向嘅人⋯但我都有少少擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4daf3a048c7a373c371bf62aec6f950b8d67337f","tid":2169330,"uid":33336,"like":98,"dislike":4,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"放心，long D 無好結果。唔揾另一個都散"},{"pid":"268b3ed95bc9bc3cd2f67352b602ea8ea3186031","tid":2169330,"uid":231583,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b52f2bce070685fdab09c47ac14df958922a0df8","tid":2169330,"uid":128102,"like":157,"dislike":4,"score":153,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:51:47.000Z","msg":"2.3個星期飛一次？<br />\n頂到半年話你好耶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721179256664c311c76d781d3a8bd000536ec82a","tid":2169330,"uid":3032,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"你價值咁低 唔飛你都偷笑"},{"pid":"c2b11b6cdce34c5cbe66b3f364ea5a06bb2f9e48","tid":2169330,"uid":117542,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"信唔過佢就真係建議分手<br />\n真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"c1cef7cdf6bf5690ec65508439c5714ca9343119","tid":2169330,"uid":313346,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"一定會，唔洗諗"},{"pid":"3be78ff56c43e95c0dc01fddeee05e5c707c45d1","tid":216